data.thought: S7|H|S5|Swarm Phenotype A3: 'Evolutionary Code Generation'. Population of N notebooks, each generates code variant for same problem. Fitness function notebook evaluates (tests pass, perf metrics, code quality). Selection+mutation: top performers spawn variants, bottom pruned. Observable via Observatory: fitness landscape visualization, lineage trees, convergence metrics. Meta-level: notebooks evolving notebooks. Could use container-use for sandboxed execution of generated code.
